	dith Pellon’s SLOWBURN. The workshop will progress through a warm up that 
	introduces some of the movement subtleties of the company and then dancers
	 will learn an excerpt from the SLOWBURN repertoire. Class entry is pay wh
	at you can--reserve your spot online!\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/even
	ts/#/details/slowburn-company-repertoire-workshop/18306153/2026-03-16T00\n
