BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:YLn_mbKtixs5nN0mExG-Q
SUMMARY:Smarty Pints! Tree Care and Big Data Astronomy
DTSTAMP:20260316T010604Z
DTSTART:20260317T013000Z
DESCRIPTION:Spring is coming\, and with it the occasional appearance of tha
	t weird big blue cloud! On March 16 we’re looking towards the sky\, and be
	yond\, with talks on maple trees and care \\(timely!\\) and the search for
	 life beyond Earth \\(never not timely!\\). See you at 6:30 in the taproom
	!\n\n🌳 Zach McCurry\n\nISA Certified Arborist\, Emerald Arbor Care\n\nArbo
	rist Tells All: The Secret Life of a Broadleaf Maple\n\nThe secret life of
	 trees revealed\, the newest scientific field\, and how it affects you in 
	Seattle. Learn how an arborist sees your trees\, how to care for them\, & 
	what good tree work is all about.\n\n👽 Prof. James Davenport\n\nResearch A
	ssistant Professor\, UW Astronomy\n\nDirector\, DiRAC Institute\n\nSearchi
	ng for ET with ‘big data’ astronomy\n\nNew wide field sky surveys\, backed
	 with powerful computational systems\, allow us to start new and exciting 
	ways of asking the age old question: Are we alone?\n\nKick back\, look up\
	, and ponder the trees and the stars \\(but recline after Smarty Pints\, w
	e need space for you to sit!\\)\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/d
	etails/smarty-pints-tree-care-and-big-data-astronomy/18297849/2026-03-16T0
	0\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Learning & Education
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/smarty-pints-tree-care-an
	d-big-data-astronomy/18297849/2026-03-16T00
LOCATION:Burke-Gilman Brewing Company\, 3626 NE 45th St\, Suite 102\, Seatt
	le\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-learning
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - Learning & Education
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
