BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:tsgseD4ccFpOjPuPNqfgC
SUMMARY:Kiss Me\, I'm Irish: Seattle St. Patrick's Day Bar Crawl (2 Days)
DTSTAMP:20260316T010604Z
DTSTART:20260318T010000Z
DESCRIPTION:Barcrawlerz is taking over Seattle this St. Patrick's Weekend!\
	n\nBarcrawlerz is a Seattle Bar Crawl like no other. Kiss Me\, I’m Irish f
	eatures The Best Drink Specials and The Best Bars in Town.\n\nThis is a TW
	O DAY EVENT!\n\n🍀 Saturday\, March 14th: 2PM-2AM \\(Registration at SPIN: 
	2PM-8PM\\)\n\n🍀 Tuesday\, March 17th: 6PM-2AM \\(Registration at Villa Esc
	ondida: 6PM-11PM\\)\n\nPARTICIPATING BARS:\n\nSPIN \\(REGISTRATION - SAT\,
	 3/14\\) VILLA ESCONDIDA \\(REGISTRATION - TUE 3/17\\) BLARNEY STONE IMPER
	IAL KITCHEN & BAR KELLS IRISH BAR JUPITER BAR PIKE PLACE BAR & GRILL SHAWN
	 O'DONNELL'S\n\nHere is how it works:\n\n1\\) Pre-Purchase Your Bar Crawl 
	Wristband.\n\n2\\) Check in at SPIN \\(1511 6th Ave\\) on Saturday\, 3/14 
	& at VILLA ESCONDIDA \\(2203 1st Ave\\) on Tuesday\, 3/14 to get your wris
	tband and map with participating bars\, their location\, and their drink s
	pecials. \\(Registration on Saturday\, 3/14 from 2PM-8PM & Tuesday\, 3/17 
	from 6PM-11PM\\) \\*WRISTBAND MUST BE PICKED UP DURING THESE TIMES\\*\n\n3
	\\) Your wristband gets you into any of the participating bars with no cov
	er\, plus gets you drink specials all night. \\*\\(Unless otherwise indica
	ted by the maps\\)\\*\n\n4\\) Have Fun!\n\nFor questions\, email info@barc
	rawlerz.com or call \\(310\\) 273-8772 Ext. 5\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.
	com/events/#/details/kiss-me-i-m-irish-seattle-st-patrick-s-day-bar-crawl-
	2-days/18305241/2026-03-17T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All Events
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/kiss-me-i-m-irish-seattle
	-st-patrick-s-day-bar-crawl-2-days/18305241/2026-03-17T00
LOCATION:SPIN Seattle\, 1511 6th Avenue\, Seattle\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-all
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - All Events
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT8H
END:VEVENT
